    "kantheon/agents/hebe/modules/providers/openai-compat/.../GatewayClient.kt:53,86-126"
  ],
  "notes": "Hebe ALWAYS streams. Reads OpenAI usage names (prompt_tokens/completion_tokens), NOT the 1.x input_tokens/output_tokens — see S2 finding F1 (contracts §7 says otherwise). Reads usage.cost and prompt_tokens_details.cached_tokens."
